HadGEM1 (mbido màkà Hadley Centre Global Environmental Model, version 1) bụ ihe nlereanya ihu igwe jikọtara ọnụ nkè e mepụtara na Met Office Tian Hadley Centre n'afọ 2006 ma jiri ya mee ihe na IPCC Fourth Assessment Report on climate change
Ọ na-anọchite ányá ọganihu sayensị dị ịrịba ama na ónyé bu ya ụzọ, HadCM3
HadGEM1 na-enyekwa ihe ndabere màkà mmepe nké ụdị, ọkachasị na-agụnye mkpebi ka mmá na nhazi zuru oke nke usoro ụwa.
Ụdị nké ugbu a bụ HadGEM3.
